##This should be a simple addition calculator. Mostly working on this to learn how to troublehoot in github for the future.

print("Simple Addition Calculator")

input_one=input("First number here:" )

print("+")

input_two=input("Second number here " )

sum_total=float(input_one)+float(input_two) #needed to convert float back to String but didn;t remeber that you need to assign the new value to sum_total

sum_total=str(sum_total)

print("Sum: "+sum_total)
